premise_source_doc_sentence: She later appeared in the coming of age drama Mermaids  (  1990  )  , earning a Golden Globe nomination , and in the same year appeared alongside Johnny Depp in Burton 's dark fairy-tale Edward Scissorhands  (  1990  )  , and shortly thereafter with Keanu Reeves in Francis Ford Coppola 's gothic romance Bram Stoker 's Dracula  (  1992  )  .
Music From the Original Motion Picture Soundtrack - Mermaids is the soundtrack album from the film Mermaids starring Cher , Winona Ryder , Christina Ricci , and Bob Hoskins .
